== 診斷的倫理問題 ==
[[File:Adolf_Eichmann_at_Trial1961.jpg|thumb]]受審時，德國哲學家[[汉娜·阿伦特|汉娜·阿伦特]]認為精神正常的人也可能進行大屠殺。]]

精神醫學對於疾病書寫（pathography）的評價不佳，尤其是未親自診斷患者的分析<ref>{{cite book|first=Susanne|last=Hilken|title=Wege und Probleme der Psychiatrischen Pathographie|publisher=Karin Fischer|location=Aachen|date=1993}}</ref>，在美國，由於1973建立的[[高華德守則|高華德守則]]，許多人更認為為這種分析不道德<ref>{{cite news|first=Peter|last=Carey|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/08/16/health/analyzing-donald-trump-psychology.html?_r=0|title=The Psychiatric Question: Is It Fair to Analyze Donald Trump From Afar?|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|publisher=New York Times Company|location=New York City|date=August 15, 2016|accessdate=June 14, 2018|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211080225/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/08/16/health/analyzing-donald-trump-psychology.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。德國精神科醫師Hans Bürger-Prinz認為任何隔空診斷都是對精神醫學的嚴重濫用<ref>{{cite book|first=Hans|last=Bürger-Prinz|title=Ein Psychiater berichtet|url=https://archive.org/details/einpsychiaterber0000burg|publisher=Hoffmann & Campe|location=Hamburg, Germany|date=1971|isbn=3-455-00740-6}}</ref>。希特勒的眾多不同診斷結果也顯示此方法的不確定性<ref>Wippermann, Wolfgang. ''Faschismus und Psychoanalyse. Forschungsstand und Forschungsperspektiven''. In: Bedrich Loewenstein (Editor). ''Geschichte und Psychologie. Annäherungsversuche'', Pfaffenweiler, 1992. P. 266; Dörr, Nikolas. [http://docupedia.de/zg/Zeitgeschichte,_Psychologie_und_Psychoanalyse#cite_note-48 Zeitgeschichte, Psychologie und Psychoanalyse] {{Wayback|url=http://docupedia.de/zg/Zeitgeschichte,_Psychologie_und_Psychoanalyse#cite_note-48 |date=20201025020201 }}</ref>。

對於希特勒的案例，特別重要的問題包括普羅讀者容易接受作者的診斷而不加思考，另一問題是若將希特勒的行為歸因於心理疾病，可能顯得他不用為自己的行為負責<ref name="Armbruster 2009">{{cite journal|first=Jan|last=Armbruster|url=http://www.kup.at/kup/pdf/8276.pdf|title=Die Behandlung Adolf Hitlers im Lazarett Pasewalk 1918: Historische Mythenbildung durch einseitige bzw. spekulative Pathographie|journal=Journal für Neurologie, Neurochirurgie und Psychiatrie|publisher=Krause & Pachernegg|location=[[Gablitz,_Austria|Gablitz, Austria]]|volume=10|number=4|date=2009|pages=18–22|access-date=2009-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703083328/http://www.kup.at/kup/pdf/8276.pdf|archive-date=2015-07-03|url-status=dead}}</ref>。也有人持相反的觀點，認為用心理疾病醜化希特勒可能造成人們把[[納粹德國|納粹德國]]的責任全都都歸罪於他，顯得大眾和其他人員都不用負責<ref>[http://www.zeit.de/1986/48/als-ein-volk-ohne-schatten/komplettansicht ''Als ein Volk ohne Schatten!''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.zeit.de/1986/48/als-ein-volk-ohne-schatten/komplettansicht |date=20191014175906 }} In: ''[[Die_Zeit|Die Zeit]]'', No. 48, November 21, 1986</ref>，例如1963年[[汉娜·阿伦特|汉娜·阿伦特]]所稱「平庸的邪惡」即強調精神正常的人仍可犯下[[納粹大屠殺|納粹大屠殺]]<ref>{{cite book|first=Hannah|last=Arendt|authorlink=Hannah Arendt|title=Eichmann in Jerusalem|publisher=Piper|location=München, Zürich|edition=15|date=2006|isbn=978-3-492-24822-8}}</ref>。社會心理學家{{le|哈洛特·維爾紮|Harald Welzer}}也持類似觀點<ref>{{cite book|first=Harald|last=Welzer|title=Täter. Wie aus ganz normalen Menschen Massenmörder werden|publisher=Fischer|location=Frankfurt, Germany|date=2005|isbn=3-10-089431-6}}</ref>。

有些人根本上反對試圖用任何方式來解釋希特勒，例如猶太神學家和大屠殺倖存者艾米爾·法肯海姆（Emil Fackenheim）認為人類無法解釋希特勒的邪惡，只有神可以解釋<ref>Emil Fackenheim, Yehuda Bauer: ''The Temptation to Blame God''. In: Rosenbaum, Ron. ''Explaining Hitler: The Search for the Origins of His Evil''. Harper Perennial: New York, 1999. {{ISBN|0-06-095339-X}}</ref>。克勞德·朗茲曼（Claude Lanzman）甚至批評試圖解釋希特勒的人，認為這接近[[纳粹大屠殺否认論|纳粹大屠殺否认論]]<ref>''Claude Lanzmann and the War Against the Question Why''. In: Rosenbaum (1999), P. 251–266; Lanzmann, Claude. ''Hier ist kein Warum''. In: Stuart Liebman (Editor). ''Claude Lanzmann's Shoah: Key Essays'', Oxford University Press, 2007. {{ISBN|0-19-518864-0}}; Lanzmann, Claude; Caruth, Cathy; Rodowick, David. ''The Obscenity of Understanding. An Evening with Claude Lanzmann''. In: ''American Imago'', 48, 1991, P. 473–495</ref>

==對群眾的影響==
精神醫師Jan Ehrenwald指出，除了希特勒自己的心理狀態，較少人研究為什麼他能得到上百萬的狂熱支持者<ref>{{cite book|first=Jan|last=Ehrenwald|chapter=Hitler: Shaman, Schizophrenic, Medium?|title=The ESP Experience: A Psychiatric Validation|chapter-url=https://archive.org/details/espexperiencepsy0000ehre|chapter-url-access=registration|publisher=Basic Books|location=New York City|date=1978|isbn=0-465-02056-9}}</ref>。在二戰期間即有人指出希特勒知道自己的心理狀態，並利用它來煽動群眾<ref>Murray, Henry A. ''[http://library.lawschool.cornell.edu/WhatWeHave/SpecialCollections/Donovan/Hitler/index.cfm Analysis of the personality of Adolf Hitler. With predictions of his future behavior and suggestions for dealing with him now and after Germany's surrender] {{Wayback|url=http://library.lawschool.cornell.edu/WhatWeHave/SpecialCollections/Donovan/Hitler/index.cfm |date=20120618140907 }}'', 1943. Online:[https://archive.org/stream/AnalysisOfThePersonalityOfAdolphHitler/MurrayHenry-AnalysisOfThePersonalityOfAdolphHitler1943240p.Scan_djvu.txt „Analysis of the Personality of Adolph Hitler"]</ref>。也有些人注意到其他有精神問題的人物，如[[查爾斯·曼森|查爾斯·曼森]]和[[吉姆·瓊斯|吉姆·瓊斯]]，也在自己領導的新興宗教團體中得到極大的影響力<ref name="coo">Coolidge, Frederic L.; Davis, Felicia L.; Segal, Daniel L.. ''[http://www.uccs.edu/Documents/dsegal/DSM-Assessment-of-Hitler-IDR-2007.pdf Understanding Madmen: A SSM-IV Assessment of Adolf Hitler] {{Wayback|url=http://www.uccs.edu/Documents/dsegal/DSM-Assessment-of-Hitler-IDR-2007.pdf |date=20190703125020 }} ''. In: ''Individual Differences Research'' 5, 2007, P. 30–43.</ref>。

另一些研究者則認為希特勒的支持者也有心理問題<ref name="Langer43">[https://www.nytimes.com/1981/07/10/obituaries/walter-langer-is-dead-at-82-wrote-secret-study-of-hitler.html?sec=health Walter Langer is dead at 82; wrote secret study of Hitler] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1981/07/10/obituaries/walter-langer-is-dead-at-82-wrote-secret-study-of-hitler.html?sec=health |date=20210201143038 }} New York Times; [http://www.ess.uwe.ac.uk/documents/osstitle.htm A Psychological Profile of Adolf Hitler. His Life and Legend] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090312083545/http://www.ess.uwe.ac.uk/documents/osstitle.htm |date=2009-03-12 }} (Online); Eckhardt, William. ''The Values of Fascism''. In: ''Journal of Social Issues'', Volume 24, 1968, P. 89–104; Muslin, Hyman. ''Adolf Hitler. The Evil Self''. In: ''Psychohistory Review'', 20, 1992, P. 251–270; Berke,  Joseph. ''The Wellsprings of Fascism: Individual Malice, Group Hatreds and the Emergence of National Narcissism'', Free Associations, Vol. 6, Part 3 (Number 39), 1996; Lothane, Zvi. ''Omnipotence, or the delusional aspect of ideology, in relation to love, power, and group dynamics''. In: ''American Journal of Psychoanalysis'', 1997, Volume 57 (1), P. 25–46</ref>，但目前沒有證據支持此說<ref>Psychological evaluations of Nazi leaders didn't show any signs of mental disturbances (Zillmer, Eric A.; Harrower, Molly; Ritzler, Barry A.; Archer, Robert P. ''The Quest for the Nazi Personality. A Psychological Investigation of Nazi War criminals''. Routledge, 1995. {{ISBN|0-8058-1898-7}})</ref>。1996年{{le|丹尼爾·戈德哈根|Daniel Goldhagen}}指出希特勒能快速取得政治力量與他的心理問題無關，而是當時德國的社會問題導致<ref>Goldhagen, Daniel. ''[[Hitler's_Willing_Executioners|Hitler's Willing Executioners]]''. Alfred Knopf: New York, 1996; Hans-Ulrich Wehler shared the same view: ''Geschichte als historische Sozialwissenschaft''. Frankfurt am Main, 1973, P. 103.</ref>。

2000年，有研究者開始分析希特勒的心理狀態是否和群眾的狂熱有關係<ref name="mmm">Matussek, Paul; Matussek, Peter; Marbach, Jan . ''Hitler – Karriere eines Wahns'', Herbig: Munich, 2000. {{ISBN|3-7766-2184-2}}; [http://www.fritz-bauer-institut.de/rezensionen/nl23/drees.htm Das Phänomen Hitler] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fritz-bauer-institut.de/rezensionen/nl23/drees.htm |date=20180620204028 }}; [http://www.literaturkritik.de/public/rezension.php?rez_id=1567&ausgabe=200009 Review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.literaturkritik.de/public/rezension.php?rez_id=1567&ausgabe=200009 |date=20180925180355 }}; Marbach, Jan. [http://www.dji.de/bibs/Muenchen01.pdf ''Zum Verhältnis von individueller Schuld und kollektiver Verantwortung'']{{dead link|date=April 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}. Lecture given on the 35th annual conference of the "Deutschsprachige Gesellschaft</ref>。

